<section class="home-intro" aria-labelledby="home-intro-title">
  <h2 id="home-intro-title" class="h1 home-intro-heading">A small laboratory for ideas</h2>
  <div class="home-intro-media">
    <figure>
      {% img
        src="Scott2.png",
        alt="Portrait of Scott Hunter",
        className="home-intro-image",
        sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 352px"
      %}
    </figure>
  </div>
  <div class="home-intro-copy">
    <p>This site is a small laboratory for ideas. It brings together essays, experiments, projects, and creative work that live at the crossroads of fields that rarely get introduced to each other: ancient philosophy, modern technology, artificial intelligence, digital art, and the study of consciousness.</p>
    <p>Most of what you'll find here grows out of questions that keep coming back. How do ideas from radically different domains speak to each other? What becomes visible when you set them side by side? Sometimes that means holding a mystic tradition up next to a modern theory of mind. Sometimes it means using AI as a creative instrument and seeing what it reveals. Sometimes it just means following a question long enough to find out where it actually goes.</p>
    <p>There's no single argument being made here, and no thesis to defend. This is an ongoing inquiry, a place to test ideas, share experiments, and surface connections that tend to stay buried when disciplines stay in their own lanes.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-blog-preview" aria-labelledby="latest-blog">
  <div class="home-blog-preview-inner">
    <h2 id="latest-blog" class="h1">Latest from the Blog</h2>
    <ul class="blog-preview-list">
      {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
      {% if loop.index <= 2 %}
      <li class="blog-preview-item">
        <p class="blog-preview-date">{{ post.data.displayDate }}</p>
        <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
      </li>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <p><a href="/blog/">View all posts</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-blog-preview" aria-labelledby="latest-prose">
  <div class="home-blog-preview-inner">
    <h2 id="latest-prose" class="h1">Latest from Prose</h2>
    <ul class="blog-preview-list">
      {% for piece in collections.prose | reverse %}
      {% if loop.index <= 2 %}
      <li class="blog-preview-item">
        <p class="blog-preview-date">{{ piece.data.displayDate }}</p>
        <h3><a href="{{ piece.url }}">{{ piece.data.title }}</a></h3>
        {% if piece.data.excerpt %}
        <p>{{ piece.data.excerpt }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </li>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <p><a href="/prose/">View all prose</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

